<div class="section_title">Just Launched: Web Portal for Tech Event Marketers and Tradeshow Managers</div>
<span class="text">

<P><A href="http://www.tech-em.com/" target=_blank><IMG height=51 src="/print/images/partners/TechnologyEM.gif" width=150 align=right border=0></A>Industry trade publication <A href="http://www.eventmarketer.com/" target=_blank>Event Marketer Magazine</A> and event agency <A href="http://www.sparksonline.com/" target=_blank>Sparks</A>&nbsp;launched an online news and information site&nbsp;for tradeshow and event marketers in the technology space. Daily news. Case studies. Best practices. Live Q&As. Just for event and tradeshow managers. Dedicated reporters and industry experts&nbsp;cover the technology frontlines and provide&nbsp;industry-impacting trends, insights and analyses.&nbsp;Take a tour&nbsp;of&nbsp;<A href="http://www.tech-em.com/" target=_blank>http://www.tech-em.com/</A>.<BR><BR>CEA is pleased to&nbsp;partner with Tech-EM to provide members with best practices and case studies online, at events and at the International CES. Look for&nbsp;the new CES Corner on tech-em.com, additional content provided to CES members from the editors of Tech-EM, and news from CEA on a regular basis. Don&sup1;t forget to download Tech-EM’s first white paper, <A href="http://tech-em.com/node/111" target=_blank>“The Power of Trade Show and Event Data-Mining.”<BR></A></P>
</span>
