<div class="section_title">CES Mentors to Your Rescue</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=45 src="/print/images/general/CEA_SBC_Logo_50.gif" width=150 align=right>How often have you wished you had someone you could turn to and get answers to your most-pressing business problems? Now you do! CEA's Small Business Council is partnering with International CES to help CEA members get the information they need to run their businesses more effectively. Seasoned industry veterans will be on-hand at CES, January 6-9, for one-on-one mentoring meetings. <BR><BR>To learn more about the program, view mentor biographies, areas of expertise and schedule a one-on-one meeting with a CES mentor, visit <A href="http://members.CE.org/CESmentors">http://members.CE.org/CESmentors</A>&nbsp;(log-in required). This service is only available to CEA members. Not a member? <A href="http://www.ce.org/membership" target=_blank>Join CEA today</A> and start taking advantage of programs like these. 
