<div class="section_title">Hotel Summit Addresses Issues That Impact You</div>
<span class="text">
In October, Consumer Electronics Association staff and 18 International CES exhibitors participated in a hotel summit with 29 Las Vegas hoteliers and executive staff from the Las Vegas Convention and Visitors Authority (LVCVA). The summit focused on various issues including: rising costs of hotel rates and food and beverage minimums, as well as future room inventory to accommodate CES exhibitors and attendees at the <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/" target=_blank>International CES</A>.
